---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="FlowDX Platform"
	description="Plataforma Interna de Desenvolvedor (IDP) focada em self-service para provisionamento de infraestrutura e entrega de aplicações."
	type='projects'
	slug='/projetos/flowdx-platform'
>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='flex gap-8 lg:gap-12'>
      <!-- Left Sidebar Navigation -->
      <nav class='hidden lg:block w-48 shrink-0'>
        <div class='sticky top-24'>

          <ul class='space-y-2 border-l border-zinc-800'>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#overview'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='overview'
              >
                Overview
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#current-state'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='current-state'
              >
                Current State
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#current-architecture'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='current-architecture'
              >
                Current Architecture
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#evolution-roadmap'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='evolution-roadmap'
              >
                Evolution / Roadmap
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#flowdx-components'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='flowdx-components'
              >
                FlowDX Components
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href='#purpose'
                class='nav-link block py-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200 border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-zinc-600'
                data-section='purpose'
              >
                Purpose
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <main class='max-w-4xl flex-1 min-w-0'>

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class='mb-10 bg-zinc-900/80 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6' transition:name='project-header-flowdx-platform'>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 mt-2'>
            <span class='work-badge'>
              WIP
            </span>
            <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500'>Internal Developer Platform</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 font-mono mb-3' transition:name='project-title-flowdx-platform'>
            FlowDX Platform
          </h1>
          <p class='text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 max-w-[65ch]'>
            Plataforma Interna de Desenvolvedor (IDP) focada em self-service para provisionamento de infraestrutura e entrega de aplicações.
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- Overview -->
        <section id='overview' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## Overview</h2>
          <div class='space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
            <p>
              FlowDX Platform é uma iniciativa de plataforma interna que visa simplificar e padronizar o ciclo de vida de aplicações, desde o provisionamento de infraestrutura até a entrega contínua em produção.
            </p>
            <p>
              O projeto nasce da necessidade de reduzir a fricção entre equipes de desenvolvimento e operações, oferecendo abstrações claras e workflows automatizados que permitem que desenvolvedores foquem no que importa: entregar valor através de software.
            </p>
            <p>
              A plataforma é construída sobre princípios de GitOps, Infrastructure as Code e observabilidade, garantindo que cada entrega seja rastreável, reproduzível e auditável.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- Current State -->
        <section id='current-state' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## Current State</h2>
          <div class='space-y-6'>
            <p class='text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
              O projeto está em fase inicial de desenvolvimento, com um workload de referência já funcionando e servindo como base para validação de conceitos e arquitetura.
            </p>

            <!-- Terminal Status Block -->
            <div class='bg-zinc-900/80 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden'>
              <div class='flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-zinc-800/50 border-b border-zinc-800'>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80'></span>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80'></span>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/80'></span>
                <span class='ml-auto text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500'>flowdx-status</span>
              </div>
              <div class='p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-2'>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                  <span class='text-green-400'>$</span>
                  <span class='text-yellow-400'>reference:</span>
                  <span class='text-zinc-300'>FlowDX App (production-like workload)</span>
                </div>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                  <span class='text-green-400'>$</span>
                  <span class='text-yellow-400'>status:</span>
                  <span class='text-zinc-300'>app + infra + ci/cd</span>
                </div>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                  <span class='text-green-400'>$</span>
                  <span class='text-yellow-400'>next:</span>
                  <span class='text-zinc-300'>cli, templates, delivery engine</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class='grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8'>
              <div class='p-4 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30'>
                <div class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1'>Application</div>
                <div class='text-sm text-zinc-200'>Node.js API com deploy automatizado</div>
              </div>
              <div class='p-4 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30'>
                <div class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1'>Infrastructure</div>
                <div class='text-sm text-zinc-200'>AWS (S3, CloudFront, Route53, ACM)</div>
              </div>
              <div class='p-4 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30'>
                <div class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1'>CI/CD</div>
                <div class='text-sm text-zinc-200'>GitHub Actions + Terraform</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- Current Architecture -->
        <section id='current-architecture' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## Current Architecture</h2>
          <div class='space-y-6'>
            <p class='text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
              A arquitetura atual segue um padrão simples mas robusto, projetado para ser escalável e mantível. Cada componente é tratado como código, permitindo versionamento e auditoria completa.
            </p>

            <!-- Architecture Diagram (ASCII-style) -->
            <div class='bg-zinc-900/80 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6 font-mono text-sm'>
              <div class='text-zinc-500 mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider'>// Architecture Overview</div>
              <pre class='text-zinc-300 overflow-x-auto text-xs leading-relaxed'>
{`┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     GitHub Repository                        │
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐       │
│  │   Source      │  │  Infra (IaC) │  │   CI/CD      │       │
│  │   Code        │  │  Terraform   │  │   Actions    │       │
│  └──────┬───────┘  └──────┬───────┘  └──────┬───────┘       │
└─────────┼─────────────────┼─────────────────┼────────────────┘
          │                 │                 │
          ▼                 ▼                 ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      AWS Cloud                               │
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐       │
│  │     S3       │  │  CloudFront  │  │   Route53    │       │
│  │   (Static)   │  │     (CDN)    │  │    (DNS)     │       │
│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘`}
              </pre>
            </div>

            <div class='space-y-3 mt-6'>
              <div class='flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-zinc-300'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-0.5'>▸</span>
                <span><span class='text-zinc-100 font-medium'>Source Code:</span> Aplicação principal em Node.js/TypeScript</span>
              </div>
              <div class='flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-zinc-300'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-0.5'>▸</span>
                <span><span class='text-zinc-100 font-medium'>Infrastructure:</span> Provisionamento via Terraform com state remoto</span>
              </div>
              <div class='flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-zinc-300'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-0.5'>▸</span>
                <span><span class='text-zinc-100 font-medium'>CI/CD:</span> Pipelines automatizados com GitHub Actions</span>
              </div>
              <div class='flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-zinc-300'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-0.5'>▸</span>
                <span><span class='text-zinc-100 font-medium'>Delivery:</span> Deploy estático via S3 + CloudFront</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- Evolution / Roadmap -->
        <section id='evolution-roadmap' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## Evolution / Roadmap</h2>
          <div class='space-y-6'>
            <p class='text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
              A evolução da plataforma segue um caminho incremental, onde cada fase entrega valor tangível enquanto constrói a base para funcionalidades futuras.
            </p>

            <!-- Timeline -->
            <div class='relative pl-6 border-l border-zinc-800 space-y-8'>
              <!-- Phase 1 -->
              <div class='relative'>
                <div class='absolute -left-[25px] w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] border-2 border-zinc-900'></div>
                <div class='pb-2'>
                  <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-2'>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] uppercase tracking-wider'>Phase 1</span>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500'>Current</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class='text-base font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2'>Foundation & Reference Workload</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Estabelecimento da arquitetura base, workload de referência funcional e pipelines CI/CD automatizados.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 2 -->
              <div class='relative'>
                <div class='absolute -left-[25px] w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 border-2 border-zinc-900'></div>
                <div class='pb-2'>
                  <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-2'>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider'>Phase 2</span>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-600'>Planned</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class='text-base font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2'>CLI & Project Templates</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Desenvolvimento de CLI para scaffolding de projetos e templates padronizados para diferentes tipos de workload.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 3 -->
              <div class='relative'>
                <div class='absolute -left-[25px] w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 border-2 border-zinc-900'></div>
                <div class='pb-2'>
                  <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-2'>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider'>Phase 3</span>
                    <span class='text-xs font-mono text-zinc-600'>Future</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class='text-base font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2'>Delivery Engine & Self-Service Portal</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Motor de entrega automatizada e portal web para self-service completo de infraestrutura e deployments.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- FlowDX Components -->
        <section id='flowdx-components' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## FlowDX Components</h2>
          <div class='space-y-6'>
            <p class='text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
              A plataforma é composta por módulos independentes que podem ser evoluídos e versionados de forma isolada.
            </p>

            <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'>
              <!-- Component 1 -->
              <div class='p-5 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors duration-200'>
                <div class='flex items-center gap-2 mb-3'>
                  <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] font-mono text-lg'>⬡</span>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-mono font-semibold text-zinc-100'>flowdx-app</h3>
                </div>
                <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3'>
                  Aplicação de referência que serve como workload de validação para toda a plataforma.
                </p>
                <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-1.5'>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Node.js</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>TypeScript</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Astro</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Component 2 -->
              <div class='p-5 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors duration-200'>
                <div class='flex items-center gap-2 mb-3'>
                  <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] font-mono text-lg'>⬡</span>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-mono font-semibold text-zinc-100'>flowdx-infra</h3>
                </div>
                <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3'>
                  Módulos Terraform reutilizáveis para provisionamento de infraestrutura AWS.
                </p>
                <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-1.5'>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Terraform</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>AWS</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>IaC</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Component 3 -->
              <div class='p-5 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors duration-200'>
                <div class='flex items-center gap-2 mb-3'>
                  <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] font-mono text-lg'>⬡</span>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-mono font-semibold text-zinc-100'>flowdx-pipelines</h3>
                </div>
                <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3'>
                  Workflows GitHub Actions padronizados para CI/CD e automação de deploy.
                </p>
                <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-1.5'>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>GitHub Actions</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>CI/CD</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Automation</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Component 4 -->
              <div class='p-5 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/30 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors duration-200'>
                <div class='flex items-center gap-2 mb-3'>
                  <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] font-mono text-lg'>⬡</span>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-mono font-semibold text-zinc-100'>flowdx-cli</h3>
                </div>
                <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3'>
                  Ferramenta de linha de comando para scaffolding e gerenciamento de projetos.
                </p>
                <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-1.5'>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>CLI</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Node.js</span>
                  <span class='skill-badge'>Planned</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class='border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mb-12' />

        <!-- Purpose -->
        <section id='purpose' class='mb-16 scroll-mt-24'>
          <h2 class='text-xl font-mono font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-8'>## Purpose</h2>
          <div class='space-y-6'>
            <p class='text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed'>
              FlowDX Platform existe para resolver problemas reais de entrega de software, ao mesmo tempo que serve como um laboratório prático para explorar e aplicar conceitos modernos de engenharia de plataforma.
            </p>

            <div class='space-y-4'>
              <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-1 font-mono'>01</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-1'>Reduzir Fricção</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Eliminar barreiras entre desenvolvimento e operações através de abstrações claras e workflows automatizados.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-1 font-mono'>02</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-1'>Padronizar Entregas</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Criar padrões reutilizáveis que garantam consistência e qualidade em todos os deployments.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-1 font-mono'>03</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-1'>Acelerar Ciclo de Entrega</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Permitir que equipes entreguem software mais rápido com confiança e segurança.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
                <span class='text-[var(--color-accent)] mt-1 font-mono'>04</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class='text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-1'>Aprendizado Contínuo</h3>
                  <p class='text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed'>
                    Servir como plataforma de experimentação para tecnologias e práticas modernas de engenharia.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Terminal Quote -->
            <div class='bg-zinc-900/80 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mt-8'>
              <div class='flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-zinc-800/50 border-b border-zinc-800'>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80'></span>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80'></span>
                <span class='w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/80'></span>
                <span class='ml-auto text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500'>philosophy</span>
              </div>
              <div class='p-4 font-mono text-sm'>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                  <span class='text-green-400'>$</span>
                  <span class='text-zinc-300 italic'>"A good platform makes the right thing easy and the wrong thing hard."</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  // Intersection Observer for active navigation state
  const observerOptions = {
    root: null,
    rootMargin: '-100px 0px -66% 0px',
    threshold: 0
  };

  const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section[id]');
  const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');

  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        const id = entry.target.getAttribute('id');
        navLinks.forEach(link => {
          link.classList.remove('text-zinc-100', 'border-[var(--color-accent)]');
          link.classList.add('text-zinc-400', 'border-transparent');
        });
        const activeLink = document.querySelector(`.nav-link[data-section="${id}"]`);
        if (activeLink) {
          activeLink.classList.remove('text-zinc-400', 'border-transparent');
          activeLink.classList.add('text-zinc-100', 'border-[var(--color-accent)]');
        }
      }
    });
  }, observerOptions);

  sections.forEach(section => {
    observer.observe(section);
  });

  // Smooth scroll with offset for anchor links
  navLinks.forEach(link => {
    link.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const targetId = link.getAttribute('href')?.slice(1);
      if (targetId) {
        const targetSection = document.getElementById(targetId);
        if (targetSection) {
          targetSection.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
        }
      }
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* Navigation active state transition */
  .nav-link {
    transition: color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease;
  }

  /* Scroll margin for sections to account for sticky header */
  .scroll-mt-24 {
    scroll-margin-top: 6rem;
  }
</style>
